{
  "texts": [
    "4.2 we introduce a novel latent refinement method specifically designed for VAR.",
    "Scale-Travel: Latent Refinement for VARIn this section, we introduce a simple but effective refinement method designed for VAR.",
    "For this, we first revisit the time-travel technique widely used for diffusion models to enhance image quality, noticing that the same approach is not directly applicable to VAR models.",
    "In turn, we propose a novel analogous technique specialized to VAR based on its multi-scale nature, thus effectively removing visual artifacts introduced by condition-annealing (Sec.",
    "4.1) with minimal computation cost."
  ]
}